=== Coherent (non-Gaussian) alternatives — required scales [estimate] ===
(a) +/-omega anti-charged admixture: apparent rotation rate of
    f+ e^{+iwt} + f- e^{-iwt} is w_app = w (f+^2 - f-^2)/(f+^2 + f-^2);
    contamination needed for each measured red shift (w=1.414):
      e=0.2: f-^2/f+^2 = 0.89 %
      e=0.8: f-^2/f+^2 = 4.43 %
(b) driven (pumped) state below the window: existence deficit at omega=1.294:
    omega_min^2 - omega^2 = +0.0383  — a coherent co-rotating
    drive of this size in U_eff (pump power, not a free eigenstate) is required;
    free dressed branches cannot reach it (see edge scan above).
(c) Mathieu n=1 sum-beat pumping (THETA_DYNAMICS WP-C): net growth at the rungs
    +0.017/+0.074/+0.21 per t.u. — rank-orders with the measured |red| shifts.

